reviewText: Mark is one of my favorite people. He is what he is and is a very open person, loves the Lord very much and shows it!!!

We like Mark Lowry but were disappointed in this DVD.  Didn't included any of his comedy, was too short and over priced for the content.  I should have read about it more before ordering.  I expected more.

I thought this was going to be a comedy album but ended up being some really cheesy Nashville Gospel.
I'm sure it's good to those who like this kind of music but it just didn't cut it for me
